latestPosts.caption:
“Mega Miss Northeast” for me has been “A Journey of Self-Discovery”

I’m still grinning from ear to ear as I reflect on my incredible experience at the Mega Miss Northeast pageant!

From the initial audition to the final tasks, this journey has been an immense learning curve. It pushed me to realize that I’m capable of so much more than I thought!

The grooming sessions were truly transformative, equipping me with skills and confidence to take on future challenges.

I’m overflowing with gratitude to have been a part of this pageant. It’s not just about the crown; it’s about the growth, friendships, and unforgettable memories!

Thank you,to each and everyone for believing in me and helping me unleash my potential!

A special mention to the driving force behind our journey - Abhijeet Singha Sir. His tireless efforts, patience, and warmth have brought out the best in each of us. His aura is infectious, and his guidance has been invaluable! He is the perfect example of “actions speak louder than words “ he will always remain an inspiration to me 🤍

Thank you, Abhijeet Sir, for believing in us and helping us shine brighter than ever!
